Package: CfDNAfragmentomics
Type: Package
Title: Fragmentomic Analysis of cfDNA for Cancer Detection and Subtyping
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Yasamin", "Nouri Jelyani", 
                  email = "yasamin.nourijelyani@mail.utoronto.ca", 
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: The package maintainer <yasamin.nourijelyani@mail.utoronto.ca>
Description: Perform analysis for nucleosome ratios comparing patient 
              and control cfDNA fragment lengths as a cncer biomarker. 
              Also, plot cfDNA length densities to visually compare control 
              and patient data. Moreover, perform coverage analysis to detect
              TFBS and cancer subtyping.
